7.post_text: Red Bull is proud to be one of the drink sponsors for SCGS Golf Tournament held at Laguna National on the 16 August 2012. It is Asia’s Toughest Test Welcome to World Classic at Laguna National Golf & Country Club.

comments.message: What is the point we submit the card? The instruction tell us only can scratch 3 box.. Must match 3... We scratch 9 box don't have 3 boxes are match!!!!! So?

Hi Jovino, sorry for the miscommunication on the instruction part, we do apologize for that. We have updated before that all 9 boxes are to be scratched and this is a chance of luck card, not a sure win scratch card. Submission of the Serial no. on the Scratch Card is to participate in the Weekly draw. Thank you.
